TXT Value: hasDescription(Lucinda Davis, "Born around 1848 and lived past 1937. Sold to Tuskaya-hiniha, a Creek Indian, by her white father. Eventually gained freedom. Worked as a caregiver for Tuskaya-hiniha's baby. Became blind in old age. Moved to live with a woman named Josephine after her husband's death. Died in Tulsa, Oklahoma, under her daughter's care.")
